Automated Sentinel Satellite Data Downloader 07/18/2017

Description:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- An automated downloader from the satellite data of Sentinel. It uses a script 
in PHP that calls the Wget() function and runs through Cron as its scheduler.



Requirements:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- PHP 5.3 or higher
- Cron 



Running under Ubuntu 16.04.1 LTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- $ sudo php sentinelDownloader.php /download/path <x_coordinate> <y_coordinate>





